companyData.description: The Online Campus Network Planer - planning mobile networks, the easy way
companyData.description_metadata_raw:
Five Bars is your online planning tool for WiFi, 4G and 5G networks. 
    Simulate the radio coverage for your campus or building and reduce costs by saving unecessary hardware.
